article.headline: Dupree's 17 points lead No. 16 Temple
article.story:
PRINCESS ANNE, Md. (AP) -- Candice Dupree scored 17 points to
help Temple (No. 16 ESPN/USA Today, No. 18 AP) beat Maryland-Eastern Shore 60-53 on Tuesday
night to improve to 6-0.

	   Lady Comfort and Khadija Bowens each grabbed eight rebounds for
Temple.

	   Kristi Veltkamp had 17 points and nine rebounds for
Maryland-Eastern Shore (1-2).
